3E%3Ch2%3EHere%20are%20Musk's%2014%20best%20quotes%2C%20lightly%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E1.%20%26quot%3BWe%20dug%20our%20own%20grave%20with%20Cybertruck.%20Nobody%20digs%20a%20grave%20better%20than%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20anyone%20is%20going%20to%20do%20it%20better%20than%20Tesla%2C%20not%20by%20a%20long%20shot.%20Boston%20Dynamics%20is%20impressive%2C%20but%20their%20robot%20lacks%20a%20brain.%20They're%20like%20'The%20Wizard%20of%20Oz'%20or%20whatever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E3.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20it's%20a%20good%20place%20for%20humans%20in%20that%20future%2C%20we%20do%20not%20create%20some%20variance%20of%20'The%20Terminator'%20outcome.%26quot%3B%20(Musk%20was%20discussing%20the%20risks%20attached%20to%20developing%20AI%2C%20and%20underscoring%20the%20need%20for%20a%20physical%20kill%20switch%20on%20robots.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4.%20%26quot%3BOptimus%2C%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20could%20barely%20walk%20and%20now%20it%20can%20do%20yoga.%20So%2C%20a%20few%20years%20from%20now%2C%20it%20can%20probably%20do%20ballet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221891%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20its%20Optimus%20bot%20appearing%20to%20do%20yoga.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511935c59fd710019eff688%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20Optimus%20robot%20appearing%20to%20do%20yoga.%3Cp%3E%40Tesla_Optimus%20on%20X%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20'Game%20of%20Thrones'%20but%20pennies.%20It%20is%20a%20game%20of%20pennies.%26quot%3B%20(Musk%20was%20describing%20Tesla's%20focus%20on%20cutting%20the%20cost%20of%20car%20parts%20by%20even%20a%20few%20cents.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E6.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20feel%20like%20digging%20a%20tunnel%20with%20a%20spoon%20at%20times.%26quot%3B%20(Musk%20was%20referring%20to%20Tesla's%20cost-saving%20efforts.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E7.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20reading%20about%20wars%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20Buying%20a%20new%20car%20tends%20to%20not%20be%20front%20of%20mind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E8.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20somewhat%20scarred%20by%202009%2C%20when%20General%20Motors%20and%20Chrysler%20went%20bankrupt.%20While%20that's%20now%2014%20years%20ago%2C%20that%20is%20seared%20into%20my%20mind%20with%20a%20branding%20iron%20because%20Tesla%20was%20just%20hanging%20on%20by%20a%20thread%20during%20that%20entire%20time.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20going%20at%20top%20speed%20into%20uncertainty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E9.%20%26quot%3BI%20apologize%20if%20I'm%20perhaps%20more%20paranoid%20than%20I%20should%20be.%20I%20have%20PTSD%20from%202009%2C%20big%20time.%20And%202017%20through%20'19%20were%20no%20picnic%20either.%20That%20was%20very%20tough%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E10.%20%26quot%3BTesla%20is%20an%20incredibly%20capable%20ship%2C%20but%20we%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20if%20the%20macroeconomic%20conditions%20are%20stormy%20%E2%80%94%20even%20the%20best%20ship%20is%20still%20going%20to%20have%20tough%20times.%20The%20weaker%20ships%20will%20sink.%20We're%20not%20going%20to%20sink.%20But%20even%20a%20great%20ship%20in%20a%20storm%20has%20challenges.%20Now%2C%20that%20storm%20will%20apply%20to%20everyone%2C%20not%20just%20us%20and%20not%20just%20the%20auto%20industry%2C%20apart%20from%20necessary%20staples%20like%20food%20and%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227332%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20red%20Tesla%20Model%20Y%20seen%20outside%20a%20Tesla%20showroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649318a51465b60019987ac0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20going%20to%20sink%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Elon%20Musk.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E11.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20people%20who%20simply%20cannot%20get%20credit%2C%20period.%20Even%20if%20they've%20got%20a%20job%20and%20everything%20is%20solid%2C%20the%20banks%20are%20a%20little%20gun-shy%20on%20handing%20out%20credit%2C%20given%20that%20a%20bunch%20of%20them%20kicked%20the%20bucket%20earlier%20this%20year.%26quot%3B%20(Musk%20was%20describing%20the%20ongoing%20credit%20crunch%2C%20partly%20sparked%20by%20the%20collapse%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20Bank%20and%20other%20regional%20lenders%20earlier%20this%20year.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E12.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20regional%20banks%20have%20died.%20Even%20Credit%20Suisse%20%E2%80%94%20geez%2C%20that%20was%20a%20shocker.%20You've%20got%20a%20160-year-old-ish%20Swiss%20institution%20that%20doesn't%20exist%20anymore.%20That's%20mind-blowing.%20And%20I%20think%20there's%20still%20quite%20a%20few%20shoes%20to%20drop%20on%20the%20bad%20credit%20situation.%20Commercial%20real%20estate%20obviously%20is%20in%20terrible%20shape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E13.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20some%20real%20Marie%20Antoinette%20vibes%20from%20people%20who%20say%2C%20'Why%20isn't%20everyone%20working%20from%20home%3F'%20What%20about%20all%20the%20people%20that%20have%20to%20come%20to%20the%20factory%20and%20build%20the%20cars%2C%20or%20all%20the%20people%20that%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20restaurant%20and%20make%20your%20food%20and%20deliver%20your%20food%3F%20How%20detached%20from%20reality%20does%20the%20work-from-home%20crowd%20have%20to%20be%2C%20while%20they%20take%20advantage%20of%20all%20those%20who%20cannot%20work%20from%20home%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E14.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20love%20working%20out.%20I%20wish%20I%20did%2C%20but%20I%20don't.%20Unless%20moving%20the%20mouse%20consists%20of%20working%20out%2C%20in%20which%20case%2C%20I%20love%20moving%20the%20mouse.%26quot%3B%20(Musk%20was%20nodding%20to%20his%20love%20of%20video%20games.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%