s%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrimea-bridge-security-burden-for-russia-despite-fixed-claims-uk-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trucks%20and%20fuel%20supplies%20are%20being%20moved%20by%20Russia%20into%20Crimea%20on%20ferries%20instead%20of%20over%20the%20bridge%20after%20Ukraine's%20recent%20attacks%2C%20the%20UK%20MOD%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrimea-bridge-security-burden-for-russia-despite-fixed-claims-uk-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Tech%20billionaire%20Peter%20Thiel%20was%20an%20FBI%20informant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peter%20Theil%20overlayed%20with%20the%20FBI%20symbol%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6530174996f7540cd05f9177%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeter%20Thiel%20became%20an%20FBI%20informant%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202021%2C%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Lamparski%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Thiel%20has%20worn%20many%20hats%20over%20the%20years%3A%20Silicon%20Valley%20founder%2C%20Trump%20megadonor%2C%20cryptocurrency%20booster%2C%20democracy%20skeptic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20yet%20another%20facet%20to%20Thiel%2C%20one%20that%20has%20remained%20secret%20until%20now%3A%20FBI%20informant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202021%2C%20Insider%20has%20learned%2C%20Thiel%20began%20providing%20information%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bconfidential%20human%20source%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20CHS%2C%20to%20Johnathan%20Buma%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles-based%20FBI%20agent%20who%20specializes%20in%20investigating%20political%20corruption%20and%20foreign-influence%20campaigns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Johnson%2C%20a%20longtime%20associate%20of%20Thiel's%20and%20a%20notorious%20figure%20in%20the%20far-right%20movement%20that%20Thiel%20has%20subsidized%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20told%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20he%20helped%20recruit%20the%20billionaire%20as%20an%20informant%20by%20introducing%20him%20to%20Buma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20Thiel's%20relationship%20to%20the%20FBI%2C%20whose%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20Insider%20but%20who%20insisted%20on%20anonymity%2C%20corroborated%20Johnson's%20account%2C%20telling%20Insider%20that%20Johnson%20brokered%20a%20relationship%20between%20Thiel%20and%20Buma.%20Insider%20was%20able%20to%20confirm%20through%20an%20additional%20source%20that%20the%20FBI%20added%20Thiel%20to%20its%20formal%20roster%20of%20registered%20informants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20close%20to%20Thiel%20told%20Insider%20that%20while%20they%20could%20not%20confirm%20that%20Thiel%20was%20a%20CHS%2C%20Thiel%20did%20speak%20to%20Buma%20occasionally.%20The%20source%20said%20that%20any%20assistance%20Thiel%20might%20have%20provided%20to%20the%20FBI%20should%20be%20understood%20as%20part%20of%20Thiel's%20gradual%20distancing%20of%20himself%20from%20Trump%20and%20the%20broader%20MAGA%20movement%2C%20which%20has%20vigorously%20criticized%20the%20FBI%20and%20other%20federal%20law-enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EValuable%20information%20on%20a%20recurring%20basis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20maintains%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20informants%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20organized%20crime%2C%20terrorist%20threats%2C%20extremist%20groups%2C%20and%20other%20criminal%20and%20intelligence%20targets.%20These%20sources%2C%20according%20to%20the%20bureau's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvault.fbi.gov%2Fconfidential-human-source-policy-guide-1018pg%2Fconfidential-human-source-policy-guide-1018pg-part-01-of-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConfidential%20Human%20Source%20Policy%20Guide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20more%20than%20casual%20tipsters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConfidential%20human%20sources%20enter%20%26quot%3Binto%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20FBI%2C%20and%20that%20relationship%20will%20forever%20affect%20the%20life%20of%20that%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20guide%20says.%20%26quot%3B%5BThey%5D%20will%20be%20either%20an%20'FBI%20source'%20or%20a%20'former%20FBI%20source'%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20his%20or%20her%20conduct%20or%20misconduct%20will%20reflect%20upon%20the%20FBI.%26quot%3B%20As%20such%2C%20the%20process%20for%20recruiting%20and%20maintaining%20such%20sources%20is%20highly%20regulated%2C%20requiring%20multiple%20layers%20of%20approval.%20Only%20people%20who%20are%20able%20to%20provide%20%26quot%3Bvaluable%20information%20%E2%80%A6%20on%20a%20recurring%20basis%26quot%3B%20are%20granted%20CHS%20status%2C%20according%20to%20the%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22824%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Pence%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Peter%20Thiel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65307fa5be9edfa8eda45cfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22618%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThen%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20shakes%20hands%20with%20Peter%20Thiel%20during%20a%20meeting%20at%20Trump%20Tower%20in%20December%202016.%20Years%20later%2C%20Thiel%20would%20become%20a%20confidential%20human%20source%20for%20the%20FBI.%20He%20was%20directed%20not%20to%20report%20on%20his%20interactions%20with%20Trump%20or%20other%20US%20political%20figures%2C%20an%20associate%20said.%3Cp%3EDrew%20Angerer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20CHS%2C%20Thiel%20was%20assigned%20a%20code%20name%20and%20an%20internal%20serial%20number%20to%20track%20his%20reporting.%20The%20information%20he%20passed%20on%20about%20foreign%20contacts%20and%20Silicon%20Valley%20intrigue%20was%20reviewed%20and%20%26quot%3Bvalidated%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20cross-checked%20against%20other%20sources%2C%20by%20his%20case%20agents%20and%20their%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20comment.%20A%20Thiel%20spokesperson%20stopped%20responding%20to%20inquiries%20after%20being%20told%20that%20Insider%20was%20reporting%20on%20Thiel's%20relationship%20with%20the%20FBI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI's%20national%20press%20office%20and%20Scott%20Horton%2C%20an%20attorney%20who%20represents%20Johnathan%20Buma%2C%20both%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20reporting%20on%20political%20ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%20is%20a%20citizen%20of%20Germany%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand%3B%20as%20of%20last%20year%2C%C2%A0%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F10%2F15%2Ftechnology%2Fpeter-thiel-malta-citizenship.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20in%20the%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20acquiring%20yet%20another%20passport%2C%20from%20Malta.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20donated%20%241.25%20million%20to%20Trump's%20campaign%20and%20endorsed%20him%20from%20the%20stage%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention.%20After%20Trump%20won%2C%20Thiel%20served%20on%20his%20transition%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20who%20said%20that%20he%20was%20also%20an%20informant%20for%20Buma%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20believes%20that%20Thiel's%20reporting%20to%20the%20FBI%20was%20largely%20limited%20to%20foreign%20contacts%20and%20attempts%20by%20foreign%20governments%20to%20penetrate%20Silicon%20Valley.%20Thiel%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2019%2F07%2F15%2Fpeter-thiel-reportedly-says-the-fbi-and-cia-should-investigate-google.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublicly%20called%20on%20the%20FBI%20to%20investigate%20Google's%20ties%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%2C%20Johnson%20said%2C%20was%20directed%20by%20the%20FBI%20not%20to%20report%20on%20his%20interactions%20with%20Donald%20Trump%20or%20other%20US%20political%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20politicians%20that%20Thiel%20has%20bankrolled%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Trump%2C%20Sen.%20J.D.%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%2C%20and%20Blake%20Masters%2C%20a%20former%20Arizona%20senatorial%20candidate%20%E2%80%94%20have%20repeatedly%20attacked%20the%20bureau%20and%20its%20leadership%20in%20public.%20In%202022%2C%20Vance%2C%20whose%20campaign%20and%20affiliated%20PACs%20received%20a%20total%20of%20%2415%20million%20from%20Thiel%2C%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20the%20FBI%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-falsely-claims-fbi-illegally-wiretapped-trump-ohio-rally-2022-4%5C%22%3Eillegally%20wiretapped%20Trump's%20phone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Vance%20accused%20the%20bureau%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJDVance1%2Fstatus%2F1624079332711825409%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eharassing%20faithful%20Christians%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20pledged%20to%20block%20all%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Department%20of%20Justice%20nominees%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20Trump%20prosecutions.%20(Most%20but%20not%20all%20of%20Thiel's%20donations%20occurred%20in%20early%202021%2C%20before%20the%20launch%20of%20Vance's%20campaign%20and%20the%20many%20false%20claims%20he%20made%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20race.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senator%20J.D.%20Vance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653082e6211def8ed838ce71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20serving%20as%20an%20FBI%20informant%2C%20Thiel%20bankrolled%20the%20campaign%20of%20now-Senator%20J.D.%20Vance%20of%20Ohio.%20Vance%20has%20made%20a%20number%20of%20false%20and%20disparaging%20claims%20about%20the%20FBI.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2F