ll%2C%20a%20genomics%20company.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fmattdrange%2F2017%2F01%2F09%2Fchuck-johnson-troll-trump-transition-team%2F%3Fsh%3D5474e3a0265e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Forbes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20Thiel%20to%20help%20vet%20and%20select%20senior%20staffers%20for%20the%20Trump%20transition%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20claimed%20to%20be%20an%20FBI%20informant%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdockets.justia.com%2Fdocket%2Fnew-york%2Fnysdce%2F1%3A2023cv02441%2F596057%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20filed%20against%20Clearview's%20founders.%20He%20told%20Insider%20he%20recruited%20Thiel%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20CHS%20and%20introduced%20him%20to%20Buma%2C%20the%20FBI%20special%20agent%20who%20was%20Johnson's%20handler.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charles%20Johnson%20with%20Matt%20Gaetz%20and%20Ginger%20Gaetz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65308922be9edfa8eda45e39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharles%20Johnson%20(left)%20with%20Rep.%20Matt%20Gaetz%20(right)%20and%20Gaetz's%20now-wife%20Ginger%20Gaetz%20(center)%2C%20in%202021.%20Johnson%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20brokered%20an%20introduction%20between%20Thiel%20and%20the%20FBI%20special%20agent%20who%20would%20become%20his%20handler.%3Cp%3ECharles%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20whether%20Thiel%20remains%20a%20CHS%20for%20the%20FBI.%20Johnson%20told%20Insider%20that%20he%20believes%20that%20the%20relationship%20has%20been%20severed%20but%20declined%20to%20offer%20details%3B%20Buma%20wrote%20in%20his%20statement%20to%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee%20that%20he%20was%20ordered%20to%20cease%20contact%20with%20all%20his%20sources%20in%20late%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson's%20ties%20to%20Trump%20and%20Thiel%20are%20well-documented.%20But%20he%20is%20also%20a%20self-identified%20%26quot%3Btroll%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20history%20of%20spreading%20false%20information%20and%20smearing%20his%20rivals.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20his%20claims%20are%20corroborated%20by%20two%20additional%20sources%2C%20as%20well%20as%20supported%20in%20part%20by%20a%20third%20who%20says%20Thiel%20and%20Buma%20spoke%20occasionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Join%20up%20or%20get%20crushed'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuma%20came%20forward%20in%20August%20as%20a%20whistleblower%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20FBI%20under%20Trump%20and%20Attorney%20General%20Bill%20Barr%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-didnt-care-giuliani-compromised-by-kremlin-whistleblower-buma-2023-9%5C%22%3Eshut%20down%20his%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20determine%20whether%20Rudy%20Giuliani%20had%20been%20compromised%20by%20a%20Russian%20asset.%20Insider%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-whistleblower-senate-judiciary-russia-giuliani-leak-trump-allies-fuks-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%20news%20organization%20to%20report%20on%20his%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20prepared%20for%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee%2C%20Buma%20said%20that%20FBI%20headquarters%20had%20closed%20his%20most%20valuable%20human%20sources%2C%20including%20one%20code-named%20%26quot%3BGenius%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20had%20reported%20on%20far-right%20figures%20involved%20with%20planning%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Capitol%20on%20January%206%2C%202021.%20Johnson%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3BGenius%26quot%3B%20was%20his%20CHS%20code%20name.%20Insider%20was%20able%20to%20confirm%20Johnson's%20identity%20as%20%26quot%3BGenius%26quot%3B%20with%20two%20additional%20sources.%20The%C2%A0statement%20does%20not%20mention%20Thiel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peter%20Thiel%20at%20the%20RNC%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653086d6211def8ed838cf20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThiel%20speaking%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%202016.%20He%20donated%20%241.25%20million%20to%20Trump's%20campaign%20in%202016.%20He%20backed%20MAGA-aligned%20congressional%20candidates%20in%202020%20and%202022.%20He%20has%20said%20he%20will%20be%20staying%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%202024%20presidential%20race.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Wong%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20statement%20to%20Insider%2C%20Johnson%20said%20he%20was%20stepping%20forward%20as%20a%20CHS%20to%20support%20Buma's%20effort%20as%20a%20whistleblower%20to%20bring%20about%20what%20Buma%20believes%20to%20be%20necessary%20reforms%20in%20how%20the%20FBI%20handles%20informants.%20Johnson%20said%20that%20he%20was%20exposing%20Thiel's%20work%20as%20a%20CHS%20as%20retribution%20for%20what%20Johnson%20perceives%20to%20be%20bad%20decision-making%20by%20the%20Founders%20Fund%2C%20Thiel's%20venture-capital%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20also%20told%20Insider%20he%20felt%20betrayed%20that%20Thiel%20did%20not%20invest%20in%20Johnson's%20own%20startups%2C%20which%20he%20had%20expected%20Thiel%20to%20do%20in%20exchange%20for%20introducing%20him%20to%20Buma.%20Johnson%20said%20that%20he%20told%20Thiel%20that%20by%20offering%20the%20FBI%20a%20window%20into%20his%20contacts%20with%20foreign%20governments%2C%20he%20could%20demonstrate%20his%20loyalty%20to%20the%20United%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20Thiel's%20motivation%20for%20working%20with%20Buma%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20hedge%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20extravagant%20wealth%20no%20longer%20affords%20the%20safety%20it%20used%20to.%20He%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Flord-of-the-roths-how-tech-mogul-peter-thiel-turned-a-retirement-account-for-the-middle-class-into-a-5-billion-dollar-tax-free-piggy-bank%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProPublica's%20reporting%20on%20Thiel's%20income-tax%20avoidance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20death%20of%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F05%2F18%2Fbusiness%2Fjeffrey-epstein-peter-thiel.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20had%20reportedly%20scheduled%20several%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Thiel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20him%20to%20join%20up%20or%20get%20crushed%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI's%20recruitment%20of%20Thiel%20as%20a%20CHS%20puts%20him%20among%20the%20bureau's%20most%20prominent%20assets%2C%20but%20he%20is%20not%20alone%20among%20right-wing%20figures%20who%20have%20collaborated%20with%20the%20bureau.%20Trump%20himself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-flipping-history-cooperating-fbi-2018-8%5C%22%3Eoffered%20to%20help%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20FBI%20fight%20organized%20crime%20in%20Atlantic%20City%20in%20the%20early%201980s.%20Truth%20Social%2C%20the%20Trump-owned%20social-media%20company%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F08%2F10%2Ftrumps-truth-social-tipped-fbi-to-man-killed-during-arrest-attempt-for-biden-threats.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equietly%20tipped%20the%20FBI%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20users%20who%20threaten%20violence%2C%20even%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20their%20anger.%20At%20least%20two%20of%20the%20rioters%20who%20showed%20up%20to%20storm%20the%20Capitol%20on%20January%206%20were%20also%20FBI%20informants%2C%20as%20was%20Enrique%20Tarrio%2C%20the%20Proud%20Boys%20leader%20who%20was%20sentenced%20to%2022%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20seditious%20conspiracy%20and%20other%20felonies%20stemming%20from%20the%20Capitol%20breach.%20Tarrio%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%