22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20is%20gaining%20momentum%2C%20illegal%20betting%20activities%20are%20also%20picking%20up%20steam%20with%20crores%20of%20rupees%20invested%20through%20informal%20routes%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20about%20Rs%202%20lakh%20crore%20to%20tax%20authorities%2C%20a%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20illegal%20sports%20betting%20market%20receives%20an%20estimated%20inflow%20of%20Rs%208%2C20%2C000%20crore%20(USD%20100%20billion)%20per%20annum%20from%20India%2C%20according%20to%20Think%20Change%20Forum%20(TCF)%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFactors%20such%20as%20digital%20infrastructure%20growth%2C%20smartphone%20usage%2C%20and%20the%20expansion%20of%20athletic%20events%20have%20contributed%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20inflow%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20regulatory%20restrictions%2C%20India's%20illegal%20betting%20and%20gambling%20market%20has%20shown%20remarkable%20growth%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%20at%20a%20baseline%20estimated%20deposits%20of%20Rs%208%2C20%2C000%20crore%20being%20for%20betting%20at%20current%20GST%20rate%20of%2028%20per%20cent%2C%20India%20is%20losing%20Rs%202%2C29%2C600%20crore%20per%20annum.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20restrict%20such%20activities%2C%20the%20report%20suggested%20strict%20implementation%20of%20the%20new%20GST%20regime%20by%20establishing%20a%20task%20force%20to%20monitor%20illegal%20offshore%20betting%20activities%20and%20forcing%20offshore%20operators%20to%20register%20in%20India%20to%20protect%20the%20outflow%20from%20legal%20gaming%20platforms%20to%20offshore%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20such%20stringent%20measures%2C%20the%20new%20regime%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20diversion%20of%20growth%20from%20legal%20gaming%20companies%20to%20illegal%20betting%20platforms%20and%20offshore%20operators%2C%20resulting%20in%20substantial%20tax%20losses%20for%20the%20government%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20it%20said%2C%20cricket%20dominates%2C%20with%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20being%20a%20significant%20driver%20of%20betting%20activity.%20As%20per%20estimates%2C%20more%20than%20140%20million%20people%20in%20India%20participate%20in%20betting%20and%20gambling%20regularly%20and%20this%20number%20shoots%20up%20to%20370%20million%20during%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20highlighted%20that%20a%20ban%20on%20betting%20and%20gambling%20transactions%20under%20India's%20exchange%20control%20regulations%20drives%20offshore%20gambling%20firms%20to%20employ%20covert%20methods%20for%20moving%20money%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20country%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFunds%20are%20funnelled%20through%20mechanisms%20like%20hawala%2C%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20and%20other%20illicit%20channels%2C%20posing%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20nation's%20financial%20stability.%20These%20diverted%20funds%20may%20fund%20illegal%20activities%2C%20undermining%20public%20order%20and%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%2075%20betting%20and%20gambling%20sites%20that%20specifically%20target%20the%20Indian%20population%2C%20many%20of%20which%20persist%20in%20their%20operations%20despite%20legal%20bans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20attract%20Indian%20users%2C%20it%20said%2C%20they%20have%20secured%20the%20endorsement%20of%20popular%20Bollywood%20actors%20and%20sports%20figures%20as%20their%20brand%20ambassadors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelay%20in%20forming%20of%20Self-Regulatory%20Organizations%20(SROs)%20will%20allow%20illegal%20offshore%20betting%20sites%20to%20mushroom%2C%20as%20without%20these%20regulators%20will%20have%20no%20authoritative%20instrument%20to%20classify%20legal%20and%20illegal%20operators%2C%20it%20added.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%