F1595789875-2644.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Figx-hopes-to-launch-contracts-for-lng-trading-next-month-ceo-mediratta-123101900731_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20building%20a%20vast%20gas%20pipeline%20network%20and%20import%20facilities%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wants%20to%20raise%20the%20share%20of%20gas%20in%20the%20country's%20energy%20mix%20to%2015%25%20by%202030%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Figx-hopes-to-launch-contracts-for-lng-trading-next-month-ceo-mediratta-123101900731_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Figx-hopes-to-launch-contracts-for-lng-trading-next-month-ceo-mediratta-123101900731_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Figx-hopes-to-launch-contracts-for-lng-trading-next-month-ceo-mediratta-123101900731_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court's%20Marriage%20Equality%20Judgment%20Represents%20Judicial%20Abdication%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F20110519%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-20-at-11.05.05-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20rejecting%20the%20right%20of%20same-sex%20couples%20to%20marry%20speaks%20of%20there%20not%20existing%20a%20constitutional%20right%20to%20marry%2C%20of%20the%20need%20for%20judicial%20discipline%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20judiciary%20is%20not%20the%20correct%20forum%20to%20accommodate%20polyvocality%20in%20social%20issues.%20Vaguely%20intelligible%20obfuscation%20amounting%20to%20no%20more%20than%20the%20intellectualisation%20of%20the%20obscene%2C%20the%20rationalisation%20of%20the%20indefensible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20case%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20much%20simpler%20than%20all%20these%20justifications%20might%20lead%20the%20reader%20to%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20necessary%20for%20the%20court%20to%20recognise%20a%20constitutional%20right%20to%20marry.%20The%20right%20to%20state-sanctioned%20marriage%20has%20already%20been%20granted%20by%20the%20same%20legislature%20the%20court%20otherwise%20seems%20comfortable%20deferring%20to%2C%20granted%20under%20the%20secular%20regime%20that%20is%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act.%20The%20primary%20issue%20before%20the%20court%2C%20by%20its%20own%20determination%2C%20was%20more%20limited%20%E2%80%93%20under%20that%20secular%20regime%2C%20once%20the%20right%20to%20marry%20is%20recognised%2C%20is%20it%20permissible%20for%20it%20to%20be%20extended%20to%20heterosexual%20couples%20but%20not%20to%20homosexual%20couples%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20question%2C%20then%2C%20was%20not%20whether%20%3Cem%3Ede%20novo%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20same-sex%20couple%20can%20claim%20that%20the%20state%20must%20recognise%20their%20right%20to%20marry.%20Instead%2C%20the%20right%20of%20same-sex%20couples%20to%20marry%20was%20being%20asserted%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20state%20choosing%20to%20recognise%20some%20marriages%20and%20not%20others%3B%20of%20privileging%20some%20intimacies%20and%20not%20others%3B%20of%20saying%20some%20people%20can%20make%20end-of-life%20decisions%20for%20those%20they%20love%20and%20not%20others.%20The%20court%20was%20not%20to%20answer%20whether%20the%20Constitution%20granted%20a%20right%20to%20marry%3B%20it%20was%20to%20answer%20whether%20the%20Constitution%20permitted%20such%20a%20right%20to%20be%20granted%20selectively.%20The%20court%20was%20not%20asked%20to%20legislate%20and%20create%20an%20institution%20where%20none%20existed%3B%20it%20was%20asked%20to%20ensure%20that%20access%20to%20institutions%20that%20the%20legislature%20has%20already%20recognised%20was%20non-discriminatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Two%20Steps%20Forward%2C%20Three%20Steps%20Back%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Verdict%20on%20Marriage%20Equality%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftwo-steps-forward-three-steps-back-supreme-court-verdict-marriage-equality%5C%22%3ETwo%20Steps%20Forward%2C%20Three%20Steps%20Back%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Verdict%20on%20Marriage%20Equality%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20fundamental%20task%2C%20the%20court%20has%20failed%20miserably.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20fallacy%20is%20perhaps%20best%20demonstrated%20by%20examining%20an%20analogy%20the%20majority%20opinion%20uses%20%E2%80%93%20it%20reasons%20that%20just%20because%20there%20exists%20a%20right%20to%20movement%20does%20not%20entitle%20a%20petitioner%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20and%20seek%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20specific%20network%20of%20roads.%20The%20analogy%20captures%20the%20very%20core%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%20%E2%80%93%20the%20court%2C%20apparently%2C%20cannot%20by%20judicial%20diktat%20create%20laws%20or%20frameworks%20where%20none%20exist.%20That%20may%20well%20be%20the%20case.%20However%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20elude%20the%20court%20that%20a%20road%20has%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20already%20been%20constructed%20here%3B%20it%20needed%20only%20to%20declare%20that%20no%20citizens%20could%20then%20be%20denied%20access%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEqually%20regrettable%20is%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20hand-wringing%20about%20how%20polyvocality%20cannot%20be%20accommodated%20in%20a%20judicial%20setting%2C%20and%20consequently%20the%20court%20is%20an%20inappropriate%20forum%20for%20making%20decisions%20about%20complex%20social%20issues%20like%20same-sex%20marriage.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20same-sex%20marriage%20is%20an%20issue%20which%20divides%20opinion%20in%20the%20socio-political%20realities%20of%20India.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20it%20is%20desirable%20that%20consensus%20on%20this%20issue%20be%20gradually%20built%20on%20the%20ground%20so%20that%20society%E2%80%99s%20acceptance%20of%20evolving%20norms%20is%20deepened.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20the%20executive%20and%20legislature%20are%20better-placed%20than%20the%20judiciary%20to%20build%20and%20assess%20that%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20entitles%20the%20court%20to%20hold%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20rights%20hostage%20to%20the%20building%20of%20that%20consensus.%20Consensus-building%20matters%20because%20it%20enables%20a%20deeper%20percolation%20of%20constitutional%20norms%2C%20not%20because%20public%20opinion%20exists%20outside%20of%20and%20beyond%20constitutional%20norms.%20State%20discrimination%20against%20a%20minority%20can%20never%20be%20recognised%20by%20majority%20fiat.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20conflicting%20opinions%20about%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20rights%20(or%2C%20worse%2C%20unanimity%20about%20trampling%20on%20them)%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20court%20is%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20that%20individual.%20It%20cannot%20and%20must%20not%20be%20to%20relegate%20that%20individual%E2%80%99s%20rights%20to%20the%20realm%20of%20policy%20debate%20simply%20because%20many%20others%20differ%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20those%20rights%2C%20and%20by%20so%20relegating%20them%20to%20the%20realm%20of%20policy%20debate%20concede%20the%20field%20utterly%20to%20the%20majoritarian%20impulses%20of%20the%20legislature.%20Polyvocality%20matters%20when%20debating%20the%20finer%20points%20of%20where%20public%20money%20should%20best%20be%20spent%3B%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20while%20recognising%20that%20the%20state%20is%20denying%20a%20group%20of%20individuals%20their%20fundamental%20right%20to%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20judgement%20does%20not%20represent%20judicial%20restraint.%20It%20represents%20judicial%20abdication.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaustubh%20Chaturvedi%20is%20an%20advocate%20practising%20before%20various%20fora%20in%20Delhi.%20He%E2%80%99s%20an%20alumnus%20of%20the%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%20University%2C%20and%20can%20be%20contacted%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akaustubhchaturvedi%40outlook.com%5C%22%3Ekaustubhchaturvedi%40outlook.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697713202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F20110519%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-20-at-11.05.05-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-courts-marriage-equality-judgment-represents-judicial-abdication%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20was%20not%20asked%20to%20legislate%20and%20create%20an%20institution%20where%20none%20existed%3B%20it%20was%20asked%20to%20ensure%20that%20access%20to%20institutions%20that%20the%20legislature%20has%20already%20recognised%20was%20non-discriminatory.%20In%20this%20fundamental%20task%2C%20the%20court%20has%20failed%20miserably.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-courts-marriage-equality-judgment-represents-judicial-abdication%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coforge%20Q2%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20declines%2010%25%20to%20Rs%20181%20cr%2C%20revenue%20up%2016%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697712979000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F08%2Ffull%2F1696786897-685.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcoforge-q2-results-net-profit-declines-10-to-rs-181-cr-revenue-up-16-123101900692_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Revenue%20from%20operations%20came%20in%20at%20Rs%202%2C276.2%20crore%20in%20the%20quarter%20under%20review%2C%20rising%20over%2016%20per%20cent%20from%20Rs%201%2C959.4%20crore%20in%20the%20corresponding%20period%20of%20the%20previous%20fiscal%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcoforge-q2-results-net-profit-declines-10-to-rs-181-cr-revenue-up-16-123101900692_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcoforge-q2-results-net-profit-declines-10-to-rs-181-cr-revenue-up-16-123101900692_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fcoforge-q2-results-net-profit-declines-10-to-rs-181-cr-revenue-up-16-123101900692_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Confident%20that%20...'%3A%20PM%20Modi%20writes%20to%20people%20of%20poll-bound%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697712804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104554647%2Cimgsize-56684.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fconfident-that-you-will-again-support-me-in-assembly-elections-pm-modi-writes-letter-to-people-of-madhya-pradesh%2Farticleshow%2F104554552.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Gandhi%20Siblings'%20Dynasty%20Charge%2C%20A%20Reply%20From%20KCR's%20Son%20And%20Daughter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%20over%20their%20dynasty%20charge%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20Telangana%20polls%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar's%20minister%20son%20and%20MLC%20daughter%20have%20said%20it%20is%20funny%20when%20great-grandchildren%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20grandchildren%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20speak%20about%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20launched%20a%20high-voltage%20campaign%20to%20unseat%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20in%20the%20November%2030%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETop%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20are%20holding%20rallies%20and%20roadshows%20in%20the%20poll-bound%20state%20and%20targeting%20BRS%20chief%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR.%20Their%20verbal%20attacks%20have%20sparked%20fiery%20responses%20from%20Telangana%20minister%20and%20KCR's%20son%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20and%20his%20sister%20and%20Legislative%20Council%20member%20K%20Kavitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20remarks%20on%20accommodating%20family%20members%20in%20the%20cabinet%2C%20Ms%20Kavitha%20said%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20who%20live%20in%20glass%20houses%20shouldn't%20throw%20stones%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPriyanka%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20the%20great-great-granddaughter%20of%20Motilal%20Nehru%20ji%2C%20great-granddaughter%20of%20Jawahar%20Lal%20Nehru%20ji%2C%20granddaughter%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20ji%20and%20daughter%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20is%20talking%20about%20family%20politics.%20This%20is%20the%20funniest%20thing%20I%20have%20heard%20in%20the%20whole%20election%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters%20in%20Armoor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Kavitha%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20saying%20he%20can%20visit%20Telangana%20as%20a%20tourist%2C%20enjoy%20its%20delicacy%20Ankapur%20chicken%20and%20go%20back.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20no%20place%20in%20Telangana.%20That%20is%20why%20Mr%20Rahul%20ji%20we%20want%20to%20call%20you%20only%20Election%20Gandhi%20not%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20This%20(name%20Rahul%20Gandhi)%20does%20not%20suit%20you%20when%20you%20come%20to%20Telangana.%20When%20you%20come%20to%20Nizamabad%2C%20have%20Ankapur%20chicken%2C%20which%20is%20very%20popular%20here.%20We%20welcome%20you%20to%20come%20here%20as%20a%20tourist%20and%20please%20go.%20Thank%20you%20so%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters%20in%20Bodhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Mulugu%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20had%20slammed%20the%20KCR%20government%2C%20saying%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20had%20dreamt%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20but%20three%20ministers%20are%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F58lbd0ag_rahul-gandhi-telangana_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20brother%20and%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20too%2C%20has%20targeted%20KCR%20over%20dynasty%20politics.%20At%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Bhupalpally%20today%2C%20he%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%2C%20who%20had%20joined%20the%20statehood%20movement%2C%20had%20dreamt%20of%20a%20state%20where%20the%20common%20man%20would%20govern.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20your%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR%20has%20distanced%20himself%20from%20the%20people%2C%20and%20only%20his%20family%20is%20ruling%20the%20state.%20He%20has%20shattered%20your%20dream%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20also%20said%20this%20is%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3BDorala%20Telangana%20(feudal%20lords)%20vs%20Prajala%20Telangana%20(common%20people)%26quot%3B%20fight%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharp%20response%20to%20the%20dynasty%20charge%2C%20Telangana%20minister%20and%20KCR's%20son%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%20that%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20was%20accusing%20KCR%20of%20promoting%20his%20family%20members%20within%20the%20party%20and%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697712540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F1lra3u8_ktr-kavitha-split_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-priyanka-gandhi-vadra-k-kavitha-ktr-on-gandhi-siblings-dynasty-charge-a-reply-from-kcrs-son-and-daughter-4496157%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%20over%20their%20dynasty%20charge%20in%20th