inst%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20which%20has%20been%20escalating%20since%20it%20broke%20out%20on%20October%207%2C%20has%20raised%20the%20spectre%20of%20not%20only%20bringing%20the%20Arab%20world's%20normalisation%20of%20ties%20with%20Israel%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt%2C%20but%20even%20making%20it%20reverse%20course.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHistorical%20wounds%20had%20been%20set%20aside%20and%20normalisation%20had%20been%20gathering%20momentum%20since%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%20of%202020%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20first%20diplomatic%20casualties%20of%20the%20war%20was%20Saudi%20Arabia%20pausing%20talks%20with%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deadly%20attack%20on%20a%20Gaza%20hospital%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20killed%20500%20and%20whose%20origins%20are%20disputed%2C%20worsened%20the%20situation%20and%20Jordan%20announced%20the%20cancellation%20of%20a%20scheduled%20meeting%20between%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Jordan's%20King%20Abdullah%2C%20Egypt's%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20El-Sisi%20and%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20West%20has%20been%20standing%20firmly%20behind%20Israel%20and%20Mr%20Biden%20said%20that%20the%20hospital%20attack%20seemed%20to%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bother%20team%26quot%3B%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20UAE%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Jordan%20and%20Turkey%20have%20blamed%20Israel%20for%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Nakba%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Palestinians%20and%20Arabs%2C%20the%20war%20with%20Israel%20did%20not%20begin%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20October%207%2C%20when%20Hamas%20launched%205%2C000%20rockets%20into%20the%20country%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20land%20and%20sea%20attack.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20war%20has%20been%20going%20on%20since%201948%2C%20when%20militias%20expelled%20Palestinians%20from%20their%20homes%20and%20killed%20tens%20of%20thousands%20in%20what%20is%20called%20the%20Nakba%2C%20or%20catastrophe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%201948%20Arab-Israeli%20War%20was%20the%20first%20conflict%20between%20the%20Arab%20World%20and%20the%20newly%20independent%20country.%20Israel%20declared%20its%20independence%20on%20May%2014%2C%201948%20-%20after%20the%20United%20Nations'%20partition%20proposal%20for%20Palestine%20-%20and%20a%20civil%20war%20which%20was%20raging%20in%20what%20was%20called%20Mandatory%20Palestine%20until%20then%2C%20escalated%20into%20a%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Arab%20states.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20military%20coalition%20of%20five%20Arab%20countries%20-%20Egypt%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Jordan%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20Syria%20-%20entered%20Palestine%20and%20the%20war%20ended%20with%20the%20permanent%20displacement%20of%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20and%20Israel%20controlling%20almost%2060%25%20of%20the%20area%20proposed%20by%20the%20UN%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVicious%20Cycle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20between%20Israel%20and%20its%20Arab%20neighbours%20continued%20to%20remain%20poor%20after%20an%20armistice%20was%20signed%20in%201949%20and%20worsened%20after%20the%20Suez%20Crisis%20of%201956.%20In%20May%201967%2C%20Egypt%20announced%20that%20the%20Straits%20of%20Tiran%20would%20be%20closed%20to%20Israeli%20vessels%20and%20this%20was%20one%20of%20the%20catalysts%20for%20the%20Six-Day%20War%20a%20month%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20Six-Day%20War%20that%20the%20Israel%20military%20launched%20a%20ground%20offensive%20into%20Egypt's%20Sinai%20Peninsula%20and%20the%20Egyptian-occupied%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20which%20is%20the%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20current%20war%2C%20over%20half%20a%20century%20later.%20The%20war%20saw%20the%20involvement%20of%20Egypt%2C%20Jordan%20and%20Syria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgypt%20lost%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20to%20Israel%2C%20Syria%20lost%20the%20Golan%20Heights%20and%20Jordan%20lost%20control%20of%20East%20Jerusalem%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20war%20took%20place%20in%201969%20and%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20or%20Ramadan%20War%20of%201973.%20This%20was%20fought%20between%20Israel%2C%20Egypt%20and%20Syria%20and%20also%20saw%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20who%20were%20locked%20in%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20aiding%20opposite%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArab%20Nationalism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20repeated%20wars%20with%20Israel%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20land%20to%20it%20-%20not%20only%20in%20Palestine%20but%20from%20other%20nations%20as%20well%20-%20has%20been%20a%20festering%20sore%20for%20the%20Arab%20psyche.%20In%20the%201950s%20and%20the%201960s%2C%20the%20heyday%20of%20Arab%20nationalism%2C%20Palestine%20was%20the%20central%20Arab%20cause%20which%20catapulted%20many%20Arab%20leaders%20to%20power%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPopular%20and%20public%20support%20in%20many%20Arab%20nations%20is%20for%20an%20independent%20Palestinian%20state%20and%20many%20leaders%20who%20have%20spoken%20for%20normalised%20ties%20with%20Israel%20have%20had%20to%20pay%20a%20price.%20On%20July%2020%2C%201951%2C%20Jordanian%20King%20Abdullah%20I%20was%20assassinated%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20one%20of%20the%20holiest%20shrines%20of%20Islam%2C%20the%20al-Aqsa%20Mosque%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20during%20Friday%20prayers%2C%20by%20a%20Palestinian%20opposed%20to%20Jordan's%20tolerance%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgyptian%20president%20Anwar%20Sadat%20was%20assassinated%20in%201981%20by%20militants%20who%20were%20against%20the%20peace%20deal%20with%20Israel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20aspect%20is%20religion.%20The%20Al%20Aqsa%20Mosque%20in%20Jerusalem%20is%20the%20third%20holiest%20site%20in%20Islam%20and%20Israel-occupied%20territories%20are%20home%20to%20several%20other%20Islamic%20holy%20sites.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbraham%20Accords%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Abraham%20Accords%20of%202020%20between%20Israel%2C%20Bahrain%20and%20the%20UAE%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20ties%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Arab%20countries.%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20which%20had%20developed%20extensive%20business%20and%20military%20relationships%20with%20Israel%2C%20was%20also%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20citizens%20in%20these%20autocracies%20were%20against%20the%20deals%20and%20those%20faultlines%20have%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20with%20protests%20in%20the%20Arab%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697711640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7ndvfk08_israelgaza-war-reuters_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-gaza-war-threatens-to-unite-arab-countries-against-israel-4496053%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20which%20has%20been%20escalating%20since%20it%20broke%20out%20on%20October%207%2C%20has%20raised%20the%20spectre%20of%20not%20only%20bringing%20the%20Arab%20world's%20normalisation%20of%20ties%20with%20Israel%20to%20a%20grinding%20halt%2C%20but%20even%20making%20it%20reverse%20course.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-gaza-war-threatens-to-unite-arab-countries-against-israel-4496053%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-gaza-war-threatens-to-unite-arab-countries-against-israel-4496053%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-gaza-war-threatens-to-unite-arab-countries-against-israel-4496053%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elgar%20Parishad%20Case%3A%20Since%20Evidence%20Tampering%20Not%20Ruled%20Out%2C%20Accused%20Want%20Chargesheets%20Quashed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19113842%2FThe-Wire-42.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shoma%20Sen%20and%20Rona%20Wilson%2C%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20have%20alleged%20in%20their%20petition%20before%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20that%20the%20prosecution%20violated%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201973%2C%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%20and%20Information%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000%20in%20searching%20and%20seizing%20allegedly%20incriminating%20electronic%20documents%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20urged%20the%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20A.S.%20Gadkari%20and%20Justice%20Sharmila%20U.%20Deshmukh%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2017%2C%20to%20quash%20the%20chargesheets%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAppearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Anand%20Grover%20said%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20is%20relying%20on%2010%20documents%20that%20were%20recovered%20allegedly%20from%20the%20electronic%20devices%20of%20Sen%20and%20Wilson.%20He%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20electronic%20documents%20are%20not%20attachments%20and%20are%20unsigned%2C%20lacking%20probative%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20electronic%20documents%20were%20neither%20written%20nor%20transmitted%20by%20Sen%20or%20Wilson%20and%20classified%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdigital%20hearsay%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fbombay-high-court-hears-petition-seeking-quashing-of-chargesheets-against-shoma-sen-and-rona-wilson%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Leaflet%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGrover%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F641904%2F%5C%22%3ESection%C2%A088A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20prohibits%20the%20presumption%20of%20the%20originator%20of%20electronic%20evidence.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Pune%20Police%20had%20failed%20to%20record%20the%20hash%20value%20of%20the%20devices%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20seizure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20hash%20value%20is%20a%20method%20widely%20known%20for%20the%20authentication%20of%20an%20electronic%20record%2C%20and%20police%20need%20to%20calculate%20the%20hash%20value%20when%20seizing%20electronic%20devices%20for%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20buttress%20his%20argument%2C%20Grover%20referred%20to%20Section%203%20of%20Information%20Technology%20(Security%20Procedure)%20Rules%2C%202004%2C%20which%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Can%20electronic%20record%20shall%20be%C2%A0deemed%20to%20be%20a%20secure%20electronic%20record%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20Act%20if%20it%20has%20been%20authenticated%20by%20means%20of%20a%20secure%20digital%20signature%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20tampering%20of%20the%20documents%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20given%20that%20Pune%20Police%20had%20sent%20the%20electronic%20device%20to%20the%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(FSL)%20in%20Pune%20to%20ascertain%20its%20hash%20value.%20The%20mere%20sealing%20of%20electronic%20records%20at%20the%20place%20of%20seizure%20does%20not%20imply%20the%20security%20of%20data%20as%20per%20the%20law%2C%20Grover%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Section%2014%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said%20the%20authenticity%20and%20integrity%20of%20electronic%20records%20that%20are%20not%20secure%20cannot%20presumed.%20To%20further%20his%20argument%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20in%202014%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F187283766%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EAnvar%20P.V.%20versus%20P.K.%20Basheer%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecase%20and%20added%20that%20given%20electronic%20evidence%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvolatile%20in%20nature%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20can%20be%20tampered%20with%20easily%20without%20any%20signs%20or%20indications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20FSL%2C%20Pune%2C%20had%20failed%20to%20answer%20in%20its%20report%20whether%20the%20electronic%20device%20seized%20from%20Wilson%20had%20been%20tampered%20with.%20The%20clone%20copies%20of%20the%20seized%20devices%20%E2%80%93%20as%20required%20under%20Section%20207%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20%E2%80%93%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20to%20the%20accused%2C%20Grover%20informed%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20multiple%20requests%20to%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20by%20the%20accused%20from%20June%202018%2C%20they%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20the%20cloned%20copies%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20still%20pending%20before%20a%20special%20NIA%20court%2C%20Grover%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20arguments%20of%20Grover%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20Sen%20and%20Wilson%2C%20assume%20significance%20as%20there%20are%20allegations%20of%20severe%20malpractice%20by%20investigating%20authorities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medianama.com%2F2023%2F10%2F223-anand-grover-bhima-koregaon-seized-devices-security%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMedianama%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Arsenal%20Consulting%20in%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frona-wilson-pegasus-iphone-arsenal%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20traces%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware%20were%20found%20on%20Wilson%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20and%20also%20said%20he%20had%20received%20phishing%20emails%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%20actor%E2%80%9D%20between%202013%20and%202014%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fsecurity-researchers-claim-link-between-pune-police-and-hacking-campa