%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20census%20issue%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20subject%20of%20heated%20exchanges%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20KCR's%20daughter%20and%20Legislative%20Council%20member%20K%20Kavitha%20had%20questioned%20why%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20get%20a%20caste%20survey%20done%20in%20the%20six%20decades%20it%20governed%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BThis%20Congress%20leader%20started%20talking%20about%20the%20census%20of%20the%20Backward%20Classes%20population.%20When%20they%20were%20in%20power%20for%2060%20years%2C%20they%20did%20not%20do%20it.%20Now%20he%20says%20he%20will%20do%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20Nizamabad%20last%20week%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20KCR%20government%20had%20got%20a%20caste%20survey%20done%20in%20the%20state%20in%202014%2C%20soon%20after%20it%20came%20to%20power.%20While%20results%20of%20the%20Samagra%20Kutumba%20Survey%20were%20not%20made%20public%20owing%20to%20litigations%20challenging%20it%2C%20the%20state%20government%20says%20it%20used%20the%20data%20for%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%2C%20Ms%20Kavitha%20said%2C%20had%20conducted%20the%20survey%20and%20the%20results%20enabled%20it%20to%20effectively%20provide%20welfare%20schemes%20to%20all%20communities.%20She%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20just%20makes%20statements%20before%20elections%20unlike%20KCR%20who%20has%20prioritised%20the%20welfare%20of%20backward%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697711400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F58lbd0ag_rahul-gandhi-telangana_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-k-chandrashekar-rao-telangana-election-rahul-gandhi-throws-caste-census-challenge-at-kcr-ahead-of-telangana-polls-4495601%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Throwing%20a%20new%20poll%20challenge%20to%20Telangana