ww.today.com%2Fhealth%2Fsleep%2Fsnoozing-alarm-study-rcna120895%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20first%20surveyed%201%2C732%20people%2C%20and%20found%20that%20nearly%2070%25%20of%20them%20snoozed%20for%20about%2022%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20the%20scientists%20closely%20monitored%2031%20regular%20snoozers%20in%20the%20lab%20to%20see%20what%20effects%20snoozing%20had%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-to-sleep-better%5C%22%3Esleep%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESnoozing%20may%20actually%20have%20some%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20compared%20sleep%20quality%20from%20a%20morning%20where%20participants%20had%20to%20wake%20up%20with%20their%20first%20alarm%20to%20a%20morning%20when%20they%20were%20allowed%20to%20hit%20snooze%20for%2030%20minutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20scenarios%2C%20the%20participants%20had%20to%20be%20fully%20awake%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20so%20they%20slept%20roughly%20the%20same%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20participants%20woke%20up%2C%20researchers%20collected%20a%20saliva%20sample%20and%20performed%20psychological%20tests%20to%20see%20how%20awake%20they%20were.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalk%20about%20a%20rude%20awakening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20results%20found%20no%20serious%20physical%20differences%20in%20sleep%20quality%20between%20the%20two%20scenarios.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20participants%20snoozed%20for%2030%20minutes%2C%20they%20performed%20better%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fgame-shows-words-in-different-colors-stroop-effect-it-2019-7%5C%22%3Ecognitive%20tests%3C%2Fa%3E%20meant%20to%20measure%20alertness%20than%20when%20they%20had%20to%20wake%20up%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20snoozing%20might%20help%20you%20feel%20more%20awake%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20be%20because%20the%20snoozing%20period%20provid