ider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-be-amazon-flex-delivery-driver-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-spark-delivery-accounts-go-for-hundreds-dollars-social-media-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20DoorDash.%20He%20said%20that%20while%20his%20current%20gig%20at%20Amazon%20Flex%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20gig%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he's%20unsure%20how%20much%20more%20he%20has%20in%20the%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%2C%20who%20drives%20in%20the%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20area%2C%20requested%20that%20Insider%20publish%20only%20his%20first%20name%2C%20fearing%20personal%20and%20professional%20repercussions%20for%20candidly%20discussing%20his%20experiences%20driving%20for%20Amazon%20and%20other%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20independence%20and%20flexibility%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20trust%20his%20employers%20have%20in%20him%2C%20have%20made%20him%20continue%20striving%20to%20be%20a%20top%20driver.%20But%20he%20said%20the%20anxiety%20of%20making%20ends%20meet%20with%20inconsistent%20work%20and%20more%20competition%20among%20drivers%20has%20been%20stressful.%20He%20says%20it's%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Btrap%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20reliant%20on%20this%20income%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20though%20he%20can't%20take%20time%20off%20to%20restart%20his%20marketing%20career%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGig%20work%20is%20still%20strong%2C%20as%20many%20younger%20Americans%20are%20looking%20to%20jobs%20like%20grocery%20delivery%20and%20digital%20freelancing.%20The%20number%20of%20US%20gig%20workers%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-economy-trends-workers-delivery-ride-hailing-apps-uber-doordash-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emore%20than%20doubled%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20still%20debate%20whether%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-drivers-explain-how-they-make-the-most-money-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egig%20jobs%20can%20be%20full-time%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20are%20better%20suited%20only%20for%20supplemental%20income.%20Barely%20anyone%20can%20get%20rich%20off%20of%20just%20doing%20delivery%20driving%2C%20Scott%20said%2C%20but%20it's%20an%20option%20for%20him%20while%20he%20searches%20for%20a%20more%20stable%20office%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavigating%20the%20uncertain%20world%20of%20gig%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20said%20he%20was%20hit%20hard%20financially%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20couldn't%20immediately%20secure%20an%20office%20position%2C%20so%20he%20looked%20into%20gig%20work.%20On%20weekends%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20retail%20data%20collector%20at%20large%20grocery%20stores%20before%20transitioning%20into%20personal%20shopping.%20He%20took%20up%20DoorDash%20and%20Instacart%20before%20delivering%20for%20Amazon%2C%20all%20the%20while%20still%20doing%20some%20freelance%20marketing%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20someone%20that%20needs%20gig%20work%2C%20it's%20great%20if%20you%20know%20how%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20sustainable.%20You%20can't%20do%20it%20forever%20because%20of%20the%20wear%20and%20tear%20on%20your%20vehicle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20he's%20driven%20nearly%2040%2C000%20miles%20with%20personal%20vehicles%20for%20Amazon%20Flex%2C%20which%20he's%20had%20to%20maintain%20with%20his%20own%20money.%20He's%20made%20it%20a%20goal%20to%20average%20a%20gross%20income%20of%20%24150%20a%20day%2C%20prioritizing%20reserved%20offers%20that%20guarantee%20him%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scene%20is%20constantly%20changing%20with%20the%20stress%20of%20being%20able%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20have%20enough%20work%20to%20do%20to%20reach%20that%20goal%20on%20a%20weekly%20or%20monthly%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWork%20is%20becoming%20harder%20to%20get%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20work%20had%20become%20much%20tougher%20because%20of%20growing%20competition%20in%20his%20area.%20He%20said%20more%20and%20more%20drivers%20are%20vying%20for%20the%20same%20few%20deliveries%2C%20and%20he%20said%20it's%20caused%20him%20to%20lose%20about%2020%25%20of%20his%20income%20compared%20with%20six%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20to%20get%20four%20to%20six%20instant%20offers%20%E2%80%94%20or%20deliveries%20that%20start%20right%20away%20%E2%80%94%20a%20day%20just%20by%20being%20close%20to%20a%20pickup%20facility%2C%20but%20now%20he's%20only%20getting%20one%20or%20two%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmazon%20Flex%20delivery%20partners%20sign%20up%20for%20delivery%20blocks%20that%20fit%20their%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20Steve%20Kelly%2C%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBlocks%20are%20dependent%20on%20customer%20demand%20and%20may%20fluctuate%20week%20to%20week.%20Amazon%20Flex%20delivery%20partners%20are%20encouraged%20to%20check%20the%20Amazon%20Flex%20app%20throughout%20the%20day%20for%20available%20blocks%20and%20instant%20offers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Scott%20said%20the%20flexibility%20had%20been%20helpful%2C%20especially%20as%20he%20spends%20time%20networking%20and%20doing%20side%20projects%20in%20hopes%20of%20returning%20to%20an%20office%20position.%20He's%20skeptical%20he%20can%20land%20in%20corporate%20America%20at%20his%20age%2C%20but%20he's%20networking%20with%20business%20professionals%20to%20start%20to%20get%20his%20foot%20in%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20at%20a%20point%20where%20I%20cannot%20afford%20to%20drop%20this%20income%20stream%20to%20focus%20100%25%20on%20my%20passion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20what%20works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20four%20years%20of%20driving%2C%20he's%20learned%20the%20types%20of%20delivery%20tasks%20that%20pay%20well%2C%20such%20as%20lengthier%20drives%20that%20can%20pay%20%2440%20to%20%2450%20an%20hour%20with%20tips%20if%20done%20fast.%20That's%20amounted%20to%20more%20than%202%2C200%20customer%20compliments%20over%20the%20years%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20Scott%20shared%20with%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it's%20not%20too%20difficult%20to%20make%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20a%20month%2C%20though%20it's%20gotten%20tougher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20they%20reward%20drivers%20that%20have%20longevity%20and%20have%20high%20marks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey'll%20recognize%20you%20with%20a%20little%20badge%20of%20honor%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20like%20you're%20getting%20preferential%20treatment.%20It's%20frustrating%20to%20see%20the%20new%20drivers%20out%20there%20taking%20up%20that%20work%20that%20used%20to%20be%20mine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20maximizing%20how%20much%20he%20could%20make%20in%20the%2040%20hours%20he%20puts%20in%20many%20weeks%20came%20with%20meticulous%20planning.%20He%20said%20grocery%20deliveries%20were%20often%20the%20most%20lucrative%2C%20though%20it%20takes%20more%20work%20if%20it's%20a%20walk-up%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he's%20also%20managed%20to%20increase%20his%20tips%20by%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20scanning%20packages%20before%20dropping%20them%20off%20instead%20of%20outside%20a%20window%2C%20or%20approaching%20homes%20quietly%20and%20without%20lights%20on.%20It%20comes%20down%20to%20small%20details%20such%20as%20where%20to%20park%20or%20having%20the%20package%20ready%20to%20go%20right%20after%20parking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20app%20keeps%20track%20of%20everything%20that%20you%20do%2C%20so%20I%20can%20find%20that%20I've%20become%20a%20delivery%20guru%2C%20and%20that's%20something%20that's%20personally%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20it%20means%20anything%20to%20anybody%20else%2C%20but%20you%20can%20look%20back%20and%20say%2C%20'I%20did%20that%2C%20and%20I%20knocked%20it%20out%20of%20the%20park.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20gig%20worker%20who%20has%20thoughts%20about%20how%20gig%20work%20has%20changed%20in%20your%20experience%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-work-baby-boomer-delivery-driver-work-harder-to-get-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697709961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6528475d6561dd877e79598b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-work-baby-boomer-delivery-driver-work-harder-to-get-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20baby-boomer%20delivery%20driver%20says%20the%20work%20is%20becoming%20harder%20to%20get%20and%20cautions%20it's%20not%20sustainable%20long%20term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40insider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgig-work-baby-boomer-delivery-driver-work-harder-to-get-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Virat%20Kohli%20Bowls%20To%20Complete%20Pandya's%20Over%2C%20In%203%20Balls%20Concedes...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20limp