e%20priciest%20places.%20They're%20in%20states%20like%20Illinois%2C%20Indiana%2C%20and%20Nebraska%2C%20Redfin%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-most-competitive-san-diego-omaha-fayetteville-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Hamas%20War%3A%20Facebook%20Rolls%20Out%20Measures%20To%20Limit%20%26quot%3BUnwanted%26quot%3B%20Comments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFacebook%20parent%20Meta%20on%20Wednesday%20rolled%20out%20a%20temporary%20feature%20to%20limit%20%26quot%3Bharmful%20and%20potentially%20harmful%26quot%3B%20content%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%20The%20change%20is%20part%20of%20the%20company's%20efforts%20to%20protect%20people%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20region%26quot%3B%20from%20such%20%26quot%3Bunwanted%26quot%3B%20comments%2C%20Meta%20said%20in%20an%20updated%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%20(October%2018).%20For%20now%2C%20friends%20and%20verified%20followers%20of%20people%20who%20create%20posts%20in%20the%20specified%20region%20will%20be%20able%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20new%20and%20public%20Facebook%20posts.%20The%20war%20started%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-thank-you-meta-israel-after-mark-zuckerberg-calls-hamas-attacks-pure-evil-4483335%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThank%20You%20Meta%26quot%3B%3A%20Israel%20After%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20Calls%20Hamas%20Attacks%20%26quot%3BPure%20Evil%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeta%20also%20said%20that%20any%20content%20%26quot%3Bcontaining%20praise%26quot%3B%20for%20Hamas%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20on%20Facebook%20or%20Instagram%2C%20as%20the%20group%20falls%20under%20its%20Dangerous%20Organization%20designation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3