0disadvantaged%20(EWS)%20and%20underprivileged%20students%2C%20as%20well%20as%20children%20with%20disabilities.%20Separate%20lists%20will%20be%20provided%20for%20these%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20notification%2C%20the%20minimum%20age%20requirements%20for%20admission%20to%20pre-school%20(nursery)%2C%20pre-primary%20(KG)%2C%20and%20Class%201%20are%20three%20years%2C%20four%20years%2C%20and%20five%20years%2C%20respectively%2C%20as%20of%20March%2031.%20The%20notification%20categorises%20pre-school%2C%20pre-primary%2C%20and%20Class%201%20as%20entry-level%20classes%20and%20specifies%20that%20the%20maximum%20age%20limits%20for%20admission%20should%20be%20under%20four%20years%20for%20pre-school%2C%20under%20five%20years%20for%20pre-primary%2C%20and%20under%20six%20years%20for%20Class%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20first%20admission%20list%2C%20schools%20can%20address%20parental%20inquiries%20from%20January%2013%20to%20January%2022%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20notification.%20The%20notification%20states%20that%20parents%20may%20contact%20the%20school's%20head%20or%20principal%20if%20they%20wish%20to%20request%20age%20relaxation%20through%20a%20manual%20application%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20required%2C%20the%20draw%20of%20lots%20will%20be%20conducted%20transparently%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20parents.%20Eligible%20parents%20will%20receive%20notification%20at%20least%20two%20days%20before%20the%20draw%20date%20through%20the%20school's%20website%2C%20noticeboard%2C%20and%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValid%20documents%20for%20proof%20of%20address%20include%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERation%20Card%20or%20Smart%20Card%20in%20the%20parents'%20names%20(mother%2Ffather%20with%20the%20child's%20name).%3Cbr%3E%20Domicile%20certificate%20of%20the%20child%20or%20their%20parents.%3Cbr%3E%20Voter%20ID%20Card%20(EPIC)%20of%20either%20parent.%3Cbr%3E%20Electricity%20bill%2C%20MTNL%20telephone%20bill%2C%2