rds%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20mid-1990s%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20was%20established%20to%20administer%20services%20in%20the%20occupied%20territories.%20The%20accords%20called%20for%20health%20responsibilities%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20newly%20formed%20Palestinian%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20as%20preparation%20for%20a%20sovereign%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20which%20the%20accords%20called%20for%20within%20a%20five-year%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Authority%20received%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farabcenterdc.org%2Fresource%2Finternational-aid-to-the-palestinians-between-politicization-and-development%2F%5C%22%3Esignificant%20influx%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20it%20took%20on%20civil%20responsibilities%2C%20including%20health.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20health%20indicators%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FSP.DYN.LE00.IN%3Flocations%3DPS%5C%22%3Elife%20expectancy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FSH.IMM.MEAS%3Flocations%3DPS%5C%22%3Eimmunization%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20started%20to%20improve%20in%20the%20late%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20it%20became%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20the%20overarching%20goal%20of%20the%20Oslo%20Accords%20for%20Palestinians%20%E2%80%93%20statehood%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2F30-years-after-arafat-rabin-handshake-clear-flaws-in-oslo-accords-doomed-peace-talks-to-failure-211362%5C%22%3Ewould%20not%20materialize%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20disillusion%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20led%20to%20victory%20for%20Hamas%20in%202006%20elections%20held%20in%20Gaza.%20Since%20then%2C%20Hamas%20has%20been%20considered%20the%20de%20facto%20governing%20body%20in%20Gaza%2C%20while%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20operates%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Hamas%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3