vacuation%20orders%20and%20at%20risk%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20uncertain%20what%20the%20health%20system%20of%20Gaza%20will%20look%20like%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20years%20past%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farabcenterdc.org%2Fresource%2Frebuilding-gaza-yet-again%2F%5C%22%3Einternational%20aid%20would%20help%20repair%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rebuild%20some%2C%20but%20not%20all%2C%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20damaged%20in%20airstrikes%2C%20especially%20schools%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20promised%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F08%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fhamas-israel-netanyahu-gaza.html%5C%22%3Elong%20and%20difficult%20war%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20And%20with%20the%20level%20of%20destruction%20seen%20in%20just%20a%20few%20days%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20just%20what%20will%20be%20left%20in%20the%20aftermath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlready%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsecurityinsight.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F2.-12-15-October-2023-Attacks-on-Health-Care-in-Israel-and-the-oPt.pdf%5C%22%3Eat%20least%2028%20doctors%20and%20other%20health%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%2C%20with%20ambulances%20and%20a%20number%20of%20hospitals%20rendered%20useless%20by%20the%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReplacing%20this%20human%20capital%20and%20vital%20infrastructure%20could%20take%20years%2C%20if%20not%20generations%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20is%20without%20the%20limits%20of%20a%20punishing%20blockade%20and%20continued%20bombardment.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F215679%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYara%20M.%20Asi%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%20of%20Global%20Health%20Management%20and%20Informatics%2C%20Uni