20reported%20that%20the%20small%20car%20segment%20saw%20a%20record%20decrease%20in%20its%20share%20of%20passenger%20vehicle%20sales%20during%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20this%20financial%20year.%20Higher%20end%20cars%2C%20like%20SUVs%20and%20MUVs%2C%20however%2C%20saw%20a%20relative%20increase%20in%20demand%2C%20and%20amounted%20to%2060%25%20of%20all%20vehicle%20sales%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20trend%20also%20points%20to%20an%20uneven%20income%20recovery%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20pyramid%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20said.%20What%20is%20noteworthy%20is%20that%20small%20cars%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20FY24%20were%2075%25%20lower%20than%20the%20pre-pandemic%20peak%20of%202018-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20of%20entry-level%20motorcycles%20too%20dropped%20to%20its%20lowest%20point%20at%201.4%20million%20units.%20This%20is%2039%25%20less%20than%20the%20peak%20in%20Q2%20of%202018-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20marker%20of%20continuing%20distress%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20and%20semiurban%20areas%2C%20gold%20loan%20companies%20are%20facing%20a%20surge%20in%20demand%20ahead%20of%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance%2Frush-for-gold-cash-amid-need-for-cold-cash%2Farticleshow%2F104507422.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20A%20gold%20loan%20is%20a%20cash%20loan%20provided%20with%20gold%20being%20the%20collateral.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20explanation%20could%20be%20that%20people%20are%20wanting%20to%20spend%20more%20this%20festive%20season%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20has%20eased%2C%20the%20rush%20for%20loans%20suggests%20their%20incomes%20are%20not%20able%20to%20provide%20enough%20liquidity.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20erratic%20monsoon%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20may%20have%20also%20dented%20rural%20incomes%2C%20forcing%20people%20to%20borrow%20against%20their%20gold%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697697058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19113729%2Fmohit-tomar-2Dss2gbE9eA-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Flow-small-vehicle-sales-rush-for-gold-loans-point-to-economic-distress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sales%20of%20both%20small%20cars%20and%20two-wheelers%20are%20at%20their%20lowest%20since%20a%20peak%20in%202018-19.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Flow-small-vehicle-sales-rush-for-gold-loans-point-to-economic-distress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Epic%20scale'%3A%20Thousands%20of%20Britons%20approached%20by%20Chinese%20agents%2C%20MI5%20chief%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697696716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104546246%2Cimgsize-24300.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fepic-scale-thousands-of-britons-approached-by-chinese-agents-mi5-chief-says%2Farticleshow%2F104546015.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104546015.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20head%20of%20MI5%2C%20Ken%20McCallum%2C%20has%20warned%20that%20Chinese%20state%20actors%20have%20targeted%20thousands%20of%20Britons%20on%20LinkedIn%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20steal%20industrial%20and%20technological%20secrets.%20He%20estimated%20that%2010%2C000%20UK%20businesses%20were%20at%20risk%20from%20industrial%20espionage.%20McCallum%20also%20highlighted%20the%20activities%20of%20other%20nations%20such%20as%20Russia%20and%20Iran%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20they%20extend%20beyond%20government%20and%20military%2