an%20who%20was%20paying%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20money%20to%20people%20to%20tell%20their%20stories.%20I%20decided%20to%20replicate%20the%20same%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20the%20world%20opened%20its%20doors%20again%20and%20Raj%20was%20back%20at%20his%20college%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20stand%20outside%20his%20college%20with%20a%20sign%20that%20read%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CTell%20me%20your%20story%20and%20I%20will%20give%20you%20Rs%2010.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20some%20out%20of%20curiosity%20and%20some%20out%20of%20their%20sheer%20need%20to%20talk.%20I%20also%20started%20to%20post%20about%20my%20initiative%20online%20on%20Instagram.%20Within%20a%20few%20days%2C%20I%20was%20flooded%20with%20DMs%20%5Bdirect%20messages%5D%20and%20requests%20from%20both%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20talk%20and%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20listen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overwhelming%20response%20made%20Raj%20realise%20that%20his%20initiative%20could%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20forum%20of%20listeners.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20Listener%E2%80%99s%20Army%20started.%20Today%20our%20non-profit%20is%20around%20600%20listeners%20strong%20who%20are%20all%20volunteers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20volunteers%20or%20listeners%20and%20the%20people%20who%20want%20to%20tell%20their%20stories%20are%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELending%20a%20compassionate%20ear%20to%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20a%20person%20can%20become%20a%20listener%2C%20Raj%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stories%20and%20incidents%20that%20people%20share%20can%20be%20quite%20taxing%20and%20overwhelming.%20This%20is%20why%20every%20person%20who%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20listener%20has%20to%20undergo%20a%20small%20evaluation%2C%20conduc