rest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20found%20this%20girl%2C%20she%20was%20in%20a%20very%20bad%20condition.%20There%20were%20ants%20all%20over%20her%20umbilical%20cord%20and%20her%20back.%20I%20immediately%20took%20her%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20treated%20for%20almost%2021%20days.%20The%20doctor%20had%20also%20lost%20hope%20but%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20girl%20was%20God%E2%80%99s%20gift%20to%20me%20and%20would%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pandey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20named%20the%20girl%20Taapsee%2C%20and%20today%20the%2019-year-old%20is%20one%20among%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPandey%E2%80%99s%2035%20daughters%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETaking%20care%20of%20Taapsee%20gave%20this%2066-year-old%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20purpose%20in%20life%20and%20led%20to%20him%20becoming%20a%20saviour%20for%20girls%20in%20Jharkhand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Bhavani%20Kumari%2C%20Pandey%20runs%20Narayan%20Sewa%20Ashram%20in%20Deoghar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20where%20they%20are%20raising%20these%20young%20girls%20who%20were%20abandoned%20by%20their%20parents%20in%20trains%2C%20forests%20or%20bushes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPandey%20appeared%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20Kaun%20Banega%20Crorepati%20(KBC)%20on%20Monday%2C%2016%20October%202023%2C%20for%20the%20stellar%20work%20he%20has%20been%20doing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20love%20of%20a%20daughter%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHare-ram-Pandey-2-1659611224-min-1697546673.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221