%20and%20his%20wife%20would%20lovingly%20welcome%20another%20such%20%E2%80%98daughter%E2%80%99%20into%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20in%20an%20%3Cem%3Eadivasi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tribal)%20area.%20There%20is%20no%20trust%20like%20ours%20in%20a%20150-200-km%20radius.%20So%20all%20the%20calls%20across%20this%20area%20are%20directed%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20raise%2C%20nurture%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328239%2Fanimal-rescue-and-rehabilitation-centres-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducate%20these%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20their%20own%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20locals.%20Taapsee%20and%20Khushi%20are%20in%20junior%20college%20now%20and%20aspire%20to%20be%20doctors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pandey%20is%20working%20towards%20a%20noble%20cause%2C%20the%20going%20has%20been%20tough%20for%20the%20sexagenarian.%20Feeding%20and%20educating%20a%20family%20of%2040%2C%20including%20the%20couple%2C%20their%20son%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20is%20a%20daily%20challenge%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%20compounder%20for%20a%20few%20years.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20corruption%20involved%20and%20quit%20that%20job%20several%20decades%20ago.%20I%20farmed%20on%20our%20family%20land%20but%20age%20has%20caught%20up%20with%20me%20and%20that%20income%20is%20not%20sufficient%20for%20us.%20I%20find%20it%20tough%20to%20put%20food%20on%20the%20table%20daily%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20helpless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20humanitarian%20struggling%20to%20survive%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FHare-ram-Pandey-3-1659610992-1024x580-min-16